Tru is a weird brand. There are currently 7 types of Tru sparkling drinks: Tru
Energy, True Focus (with l-theanine) and Tru Defend (immune system support), Tru
Dream (chamomile, gaba, magnesium), Tru Gut, Tru Refresh, Tru Glow (biotin).
Founded originally in 2015, Tru expanded to the current sparkling energy drink
lineup in 2021 from only offering energy shots before.

Yesterday was the first day I saw this brand on shelves, at a Dollar Tree no
less; I bought both varieties they had, the other being
[[Tru_Energy_Orange_Mango]], and some other weird energy drinks too.

I was wary of the minimalist design of the can, drinks like this tend to be hit
or miss.

<figure>
[[!template id="hooya-img.tmpl" cid="bafkreic2m2bbfdorq2gwwjkfgq35e5oayy5okgraij2j6yrfjmgxost5im" size=medium]]
